# The /vision folder is DevLab's Vision Catalog for this service: idea deposits —
# specs, mindmaps, screenshots, PDFs, notes — that collaborators attach and discuss.
# DevLab reads this folder from the repo, so keep curated vision material TRACKED
# (git.Tree honours .gitignore, so anything ignored here is invisible in DevLab).
#
# Ignore only throwaway/derived junk, never real vision docs:
*.tmp
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
node_modules/
# Local render caches (e.g. exported previews) — keep the source, drop the derived:
.cache/
*.render.*
